---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const seo = {"title": "Dermal Fillers — Juvederm® Collection | D‑Essence Wellness", "description": "Hyaluronic acid fillers for lift, contour, and refined smoothing.", "canonical": "/services/juvederm-fillers", "type": "website", "ogImage": "/og-default" };
---

<BaseLayout {...seo}>

<section class="relative isolate paper">

<style is:global>
  :root{
    --paper:#F8F6F2; --ink:#141414; --muted:#5a5a5a; --rule:#E6E1D8;
  }
  .paper{ background:var(--paper); color:var(--ink); }
  .rule{ border-color:var(--rule); }
  .muted{ color:var(--muted); }
  .measure{ max-width: 64ch; }
  .dropcap:first-letter{ float:left; font-size:3.2rem; line-height:1; padding-right:.35rem; padding-top:.2rem; font-weight:600; }
  .ataglance{ display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:.75rem 1.25rem; font-size:.95rem; color:var(--muted); }
  .ataglance span::after{ content:"·"; margin-left:1.25rem; color:var(--muted); }
  .ataglance span:last-child::after{ content:""; margin:0; }
  .pullquote{ border-left:2px solid var(--ink); padding-left:.85rem; font-style:italic; color:#3b3b3b; margin: 1.25rem 0; }
  @media (max-width: 1023px){ .side-col{ display:none; } }
  details.faq summary{ list-style:none; }
  details.faq summary::-webkit-details-marker{ display:none; }
  .faq-toggle{ width:1.1rem; height:1.1rem; margin-right:.5rem; flex:0 0 auto; }
  details.faq[open] .plus{ display:none; }
  details.faq:not([open]) .minus{ display:none; }
  .icon-check{ width:1.1rem; height:1.1rem; flex:0 0 auto; margin-top:.15rem;}
  .timeline{ position:relative; }
  .timeline::before{ content:""; position:absolute; left:.9rem; top:.25rem; bottom:.25rem; width:2px; background:var(--rule); }
  .tl-step{ position:relative; padding-left:2.25rem; }
  .tl-badge{ position:absolute; left:0; top:.1rem; width:1.8rem; height:1.8rem; border-radius:999px; background:var(--ink); color:#fff; font-size:.9rem; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-weight:600; }
  .tl-title{ font-weight:600; }
</style>

  <!-- HERO (left‑aligned, no breadcrumb) -->
  <div class="px-6 pt-28 md:pt-32 pb-10">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <p class="text-xs tracking-wider uppercase muted">Service</p>
      <h1 class="mt-2 text-[2.75rem] md:text-6xl leading-[1.05] font-semibold tracking-tight">Dermal Fillers — Juvederm® Collection</h1>
      <p class="mt-3 text-[1.125rem] md:text-xl muted measure">Hyaluronic acid fillers for lift, contour, and refined smoothing.</p>
      <div class="mt-6 h-px w-full border-t rule"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- BODY -->
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 pb-24 grid grid-cols-12 gap-8">

    <!-- Removed left side labels entirely -->

    <!-- Main narrative -->
    <article class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-8 xl:col-span-7">
      <!-- DESCRIPTION (unique, professional) -->
      <section id="description" class="measure">
<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Description</h2><p class="mt-3 muted dropcap">Juvéderm® is a collection of FDA‑approved hyaluronic acid (HA) dermal fillers used to restore volume, smooth static lines, and enhance facial contours. The smooth HA gel integrates with your tissue to deliver immediate, natural‑looking results without surgery.</p><p class="mt-3 muted">The collection includes specialized formulas for different goals and areas (e.g., lips, cheeks, folds, chin/jawline). Your provider selects the right product and technique to match your anatomy and desired outcome.</p>
</section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <!-- BENEFITS (unchanged from v2) -->
      <section id="benefits" class="measure">
<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Benefits</h2><ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 list-disc pl-5"><li><strong>Immediate improvement:</strong> visible softening of lines and restoration of volume right after treatment.</li><li><strong>Minimal downtime:</strong> most people return to normal activities the same day.</li><li><strong>Natural finish:</strong> HA gel blends seamlessly for soft, flexible movement.</li><li><strong>Longevity:</strong> depending on product/area, results commonly last ~6–18 months (some up to ~2 years).</li><li><strong>Versatility:</strong> lips, cheeks, nasolabial folds, marionette lines, chin, jawline, and more.</li><li><strong>Biocompatible:</strong> HA occurs naturally in the body and is well‑tolerated.</li></ul>
</section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <!-- THE PROCESS (unchanged from v2) -->
      <section id="process" class="measure">
<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">The Process</h2><ol class="mt-4 space-y-2 list-decimal pl-5"><li><strong>Consultation:</strong> Facial assessment, medical history, and personalized plan.</li><li><strong>Preparation:</strong> Cleansing + topical numbing; Juvéderm contains lidocaine for comfort.</li><li><strong>Injection:</strong> Precise placement with needle or cannula; gentle shaping for smooth contours (≈15–30 min).</li><li><strong>Immediate results:</strong> volume is visible right away; mild swelling/redness can occur.</li><li><strong>Follow‑up:</strong> Optional check around 2 weeks once swelling has settled.</li></ol>
</section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <!-- PRE / POST (unchanged from v2) -->
      <section id="care" class="measure">
<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Pre and Post‑Treatment Instructions</h2>
<h3 class="mt-4 font-semibold">Before</h3>
<ul class="mt-2 space-y-2 list-disc pl-5">
  <li>Avoid blood‑thinning meds/supplements (aspirin, NSAIDs, fish oil, vitamin E) ~7 days unless prescribed—consult your provider.</li>
  <li>No alcohol for 24 hours prior.</li>
  <li>Reschedule if you have active skin infection/cold sore in the area.</li>
  <li>Not suitable if pregnant, breastfeeding, or allergic to lidocaine.</li>
</ul>
<h3 class="mt-4 font-semibold">After</h3>
<ul class="mt-2 space-y-2 list-disc pl-5">
  <li>Remain upright for ~4 hours; avoid pressing or massaging the area the first day (unless instructed).</li>
  <li>Apply cool packs intermittently; expect temporary swelling/bruise (usually resolves within a week).</li>
  <li>Avoid strenuous exercise, heat/sauna, and alcohol for 24 hours.</li>
  <li>No facials/laser on the area for 1–2 weeks unless cleared by your provider.</li>
</ul>
</section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <!-- FAQs (unchanged from v2) -->
      <section id="faqs" class="measure">
<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
<h3 class="mt-4 font-semibold">How is Juvéderm different from Botox?</h3>
<p class="mt-2 muted">Juvéderm adds volume to smooth lines and enhance features; Botox relaxes muscles that cause dynamic wrinkles. They are often combined for comprehensive rejuvenation.</p>
<h3 class="mt-4 font-semibold">How long do results last?</h3>
<p class="mt-2 muted">Typically ~6–18 months depending on product/area and individual metabolism; some formulations can approach ~2 years with optimal placement.</p>
<h3 class="mt-4 font-semibold">What areas can be treated?</h3>
<p class="mt-2 muted">Lips, cheeks, nasolabial folds, marionette lines, chin, jawline, and select tear‑trough candidates.</p>
<h3 class="mt-4 font-semibold">Is it safe?</h3>
<p class="mt-2 muted">Hyaluronic acid is biocompatible and well‑tolerated. Common effects are temporary swelling/bruising. Rare risks exist—choose an experienced injector.</p>
<h3 class="mt-4 font-semibold">Does it hurt?</h3>
<p class="mt-2 muted">Discomfort is usually minimal thanks to topical numbing and lidocaine within the filler.</p>
<h3 class="mt-4 font-semibold">Will I see results right away?</h3>
<p class="mt-2 muted">Yes—improvements are immediate, with refinement as swelling subsides over a few days. Downtime is typically minimal.</p>
</section>
    </article>

    <!-- Right margin notes (sticky cues) remain -->
    <aside class="side-col col-span-2 lg:col-span-3 xl:col-span-4">
      <div class="sticky-top measure">
        <p class="muted"><strong>Good to know:</strong> Technique, cadence, and aftercare are tailored to your timeline.</p>
        <p class="muted mt-4"><strong>Quality:</strong> Trained providers, premium sourcing, evidence‑informed protocols.</p>
        <p class="muted mt-4"><strong>Expectations:</strong> Realistic timelines and clear check‑ins.</p>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>
